            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "今日我咁睇｜美伊談判方向未變 油價反映一切 恒指望試26000點 ｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vg8yL47a5zhIBS2Pz1P1XQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/fc66ce2e16cec7a4ff8b5028b04c8958\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.周末美伊談判未成功，實際上並不出小編的預期，皆因一開始談判都是互相開天殺價，不過市場就驚又要打過，加上到美軍威脅封鎖海峽，令昨日股市下跌、油價向上，不過不用看兩方政府如何說，只需看油價上落即可，油價升幅有限，即談判尚未破裂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.其後美國副總統便表示有進展，而東道主巴基斯坦則預期16日會重啟第二輪談判，加上戰火未有加劇，雖然未停火，但實際上已開始停火。伊朗固然損失慘重，但美國戰場勝了戰略卻未贏，加上內部政治壓力加劇，都促使雙方不願意但需要停手。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ad15296c-5f3a-3031-85a9-ad432752901c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 恒指估計今日在25800點上上落，若企穩26000點可追，若未有破位則值博率一般，暫時按兵不動，若重倉則可先賣出一些。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4.選股方面，Minimax、智譜等AI大模型股尚未見轉勢，可以續追，電動車股比亞迪油價跌時跌幅不大，昨日則升勢十足，可以考慮買入作對沖。單買指數則如上所言，值博率不高，不宜急追。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證約55%，在今日殺一輪熊證後或有增加，觀望是否能維持較低的水平，暫時啟示度不大。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E6%9C%AA%E8%AE%8A-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0-%E5%88%87-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9B%E8%A9%A626000%E9%BB%9E-020000077.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 10:08:08",
